        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your body proves capable of truly heroic feats, but doing so interferes with your mental focus.</p>\n<p>You take a -2 status penalty to AC and saving throws, and are @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Stupefied]{Stupefied 2}.</p>\n<p>You gain a +6 status bonus to weapon and unarmed damage rolls, and a +1 status bonus to weapon and unarmed attack rolls.</p>\n<p>You also gain fast healing equal to your level while in a non-trivial combat encounter.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><em>Note: You need to apply the stupefied condition and fast healing manually. The remaining effects are applied automatically.</em></p>"
